y a (column,row) pair.</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/7.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ActCode.html#v3-ActCode-POLY\">POLY</a></td><td>Multi</td><td>A series of connected line segments with ordered vertices denoted by (column,row) pairs; if the first and last vertices are the same, it is a closed polygon.</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
